00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:35,007
Come on, Philippe,
it's a shortcut.

269
00:11:35,041 --> 00:11:36,531
We'll be there in no time.

270
00:11:49,222 --> 00:11:52,680
( creatures calling )

271
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:55,284
( alarmed nickering )

272
00:11:55,328 --> 00:11:56,886
This can't be right.

273
00:11:56,929 --> 00:11:59,625
Where have you taken us,
Philippe?

274
00:11:59,665 --> 00:12:02,463
