278
00:12:09,142 --> 00:12:10,803
Oh...!

279
00:12:10,843 --> 00:12:12,412
Oh, look out!

280
00:12:12,412 --> 00:12:12,639
Oh, look out!

281
00:12:12,678 --> 00:12:14,373
