282
00:12:16,382 --> 00:12:18,009
Whoa!

283
00:12:18,051 --> 00:12:20,019
Whoa, boy!

284
00:12:20,053 --> 00:12:22,886
Back up, back up, back up!

285
00:12:22,922 --> 00:12:24,981
Good boy, good boy.

286
00:12:25,024 --> 00:12:26,048
That's it.

287
00:12:26,092 --> 00:12:27,116
Back up!

288
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:28,889
Steady, steady.

289
00:12:28,928 --> 00:12:29,986
Now, steady.

290
00:12:30,029 --> 00:12:31,360
( wolf howling )

291
00:12:31,397 --> 00:12:32,386
( whinnying )

292
00:12:32,432 --> 00:12:34,195
Philippe, no!

293
00:12:40,139 --> 00:12:41,470
Philippe.

294
00:12:41,507 --> 00:12:44,305
( thunder rumbling )

295
00:12:44,343 --> 00:12:46,140
Oh...

296
00:12:49,048 --> 00:12:52,040
( menacing growls )

297
00:12:52,085 --> 00:12:54,212
( gasping )

298
00:12:54,253 --> 00:12:55,550
( growling )

299
00:12:55,588 --> 00:12:59,319
( wolf howling )

300
